  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"..\\images\\W.gif\"/><b>\n        Greenwich</b><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>Greenwich is a borough in London on the south side of\n        the Thames; opposite is the Isle of Dogs (a peninsula):\n        Eliot presumably intends a reference to the earlier theme\n        of the Dog. (NA)</p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td> </td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "Greenwich Greenwich is a borough in London on the south side of the Thames; opposite is the Isle of Dogs (a peninsula): Eliot presumably intends a reference to the earlier theme of the Dog. (NA) reference topics back to \"The Waste Land\"",
